{"id":726,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":726,"title":"Isaiah 24","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 24"],[".studySummary",["i","Men will transgress the law and break the everlasting covenant—At the Second Coming, they will be burned, the earth will reel, and the sun will be ashamed—Then the Lord will reign in Zion and in Jerusalem."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.1","order":"02.24.024.46955"},["b","1"],"Behold, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"maketh the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"earth"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"empty"],", and maketh it waste, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"turneth"],"it upside down, and scattereth abroad the inhabitants thereof."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.2","order":"02.24.024.46956"},["b","2"],"And it shall be, as with the people, so with the priest; as with the servant, so with his master; as with the maid, so with her mistress; as with the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"buyer"],", so with the seller; as with the lender, so with the borrower; as with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"the"],"taker of usury, so with the giver of usury to him."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.3","order":"02.24.024.46957"},["b","3"],"The land shall be utterly emptied, and utterly spoiled: for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath spoken this word."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.4","order":"02.24.024.46958"},["b","4"],"The earth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"mourneth"],["i","and"],"fadeth away, the world languisheth",["i","and"],"fadeth away,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"the"],"haughty people of the earth do languish."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.5","order":"02.24.024.46959"},["b","5"],"The earth also is defiled under the inhabitants thereof; because they have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"transgressed"],"the laws,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"changed"],"the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"ordinance"],",",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_5d"},"broken"],"the",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_5e"},"everlasting"],["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_5f"},"covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.6","order":"02.24.024.46960"},["b","6"],"Therefore hath the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"curse"],"devoured the earth, and they that dwell therein are desolate: therefore the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"inhabitants"],"of the earth are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"burned"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"few"],"men left."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.7","order":"02.24.024.46961"},["b","7"],"The new wine mourneth, the vine languisheth, all the merryhearted do sigh."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.8","order":"02.24.024.46962"},["b","8"],"The mirth of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"tabrets"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"ceaseth"],", the noise of them that rejoice endeth, the joy of the harp ceaseth."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.9","order":"02.24.024.46963"},["b","9"],"They shall not drink wine with a song; strong",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"drink"],"shall be bitter to them that drink it."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.10","order":"02.24.024.46964"},["b","10"],"The city of confusion is broken down: every house is shut up, that no man may come in."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.11","order":"02.24.024.46965"},["b","11"],["i","There is"],"a crying for wine in the streets; all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"joy"],"is darkened, the mirth of the land is gone."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.12","order":"02.24.024.46966"},["b","12"],"In the city is left desolation, and the gate is smitten with destruction."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.13","order":"02.24.024.46967"},["b","13"],"¶When thus it shall be in the midst of the land among the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"people"],",",["i","there shall be"],"as the shaking of an olive tree,",["i","and"],"as the gleaning grapes when the vintage is done."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.14","order":"02.24.024.46968"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"They"],"shall lift up their voice, they shall sing for the majesty of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", they shall cry aloud from the sea."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.15","order":"02.24.024.46969"},["b","15"],"Wherefore glorify ye the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"fires"],",",["i","even"],"the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of Israel in the isles of the sea."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.16","order":"02.24.024.46970"},["b","16"],"¶From the uttermost part of the earth have we heard songs,",["i","even"],"glory to the righteous. But I said,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"My"],"leanness, my leanness, woe unto me! the treacherous dealers have dealt treacherously; yea,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"the"],"treacherous dealers have dealt very treacherously."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.17","order":"02.24.024.46971"},["b","17"],"Fear, and the pit, and the snare,",["i","are"],"upon thee, O inhabitant of the earth."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.18","order":"02.24.024.46972"},["b","18"],"And it shall come to pass,",["i","that"],"he who fleeth from the noise of the fear shall fall into the pit; and he that cometh up out of the midst of the pit shall be taken in the snare: for the windows from on high are open, and the foundations of the earth do shake."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.19","order":"02.24.024.46973"},["b","19"],"The earth is utterly broken down, the earth is clean dissolved, the earth is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"moved"],"exceedingly."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.20","order":"02.24.024.46974"},["b","20"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"earth"],"shall reel to and fro like a drunkard, and shall be removed like a cottage; and the transgression thereof shall be heavy upon it; and it shall fall, and not rise again."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.21","order":"02.24.024.46975"},["b","21"],"And it shall come to pass in that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"day"],",",["i","that"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"punish"],"the host of the high ones",["i","that are"],"on high, and the kings of the earth upon the earth."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.22","order":"02.24.024.46976"},["b","22"],"And they shall be gathered together,",["i","as"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"prisoners"],"are gathered in the pit, and shall be shut up in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"prison"],", and after many days shall they be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"visited"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.23","order":"02.24.024.46977"},["b","23"],"Then the moon shall be confounded, and the sun",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"ashamed"],", when the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts shall reign in mount",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"Zion"],", and in Jerusalem, and before",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"his ancients gloriously"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.1a","order":"02.24.024.46978"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.13"},"Isa. 13:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.1b","order":"02.24.024.46980"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.19"},"D&C 5:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.1c","order":"02.24.024.46982"},["b","1c"],["span.small","IE"],"when the whole wicked world shall end."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.2a","order":"02.24.024.46984"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.12"},"Ezek. 7:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.2b","order":"02.24.024.46986"},["b","2b"],["span.small","OR"],"him who exacts payment, so with him who makes payment.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/usury"},"TG Usury"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.4a","order":"02.24.024.46988"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mourning"},"TG Mourning"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.4b","order":"02.24.024.46990"},["b","4b"],["span.small","OR"],"the upper classes are despondent."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.5a","order":"02.24.024.46992"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.5b","order":"02.24.024.46994"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.15"},"D&C 1:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.5c","order":"02.24.024.46996"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/ordinance"},"TG Ordinance"],"."],["div",{"id":"5d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.5d","order":"02.24.024.46998"},["b","5d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-individuals"},"TG Apostasy of Individuals"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-israel"},"Apostasy of Israel"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-the-early-christian-church"},"Apostasy of the Early Christian Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"5e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.5e","order":"02.24.024.47000"},["b","5e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/new-and-everlasting-covenant"},"TG New and Everlasting Covenant"],"."],["div",{"id":"5f","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.5f","order":"02.24.024.47002"},["b","5f"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/covenants"},"TG Covenants"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.6a","order":"02.24.024.47004"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/curse"},"TG Curse"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-curse-of"},"Earth, Curse of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.6b","order":"02.24.024.47006"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/17.2"},"Rev. 17:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.17"},"D&C 1:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.6c","order":"02.24.024.47008"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/day-of-the-lord"},"TG Day of the Lord"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-cleansing-of"},"Earth, Cleansing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.6d","order":"02.24.024.47010"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.12"},"Isa. 13:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.8a","order":"02.24.024.47012"},["b","8a"],["span.small","HEB"],"drums."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.8b","order":"02.24.024.47014"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.11"},"Hosea 2:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.9a","order":"02.24.024.47016"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/word-of-wisdom"},"TG Word of Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.11a","order":"02.24.024.47018"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/1.12.11-13"},"Joel 1:12 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.13a","order":"02.24.024.47020"},["b","13a"],["span.small","HEB"],"peoples or nations."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.14a","order":"02.24.024.47022"},["b","14a"],["span.small","IE"],"The righteous remnant."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.15a","order":"02.24.024.47024"},["b","15a"],["span.small","HEB"],"lights; or perhaps a scribal error for “islands.”"],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.16a","order":"02.24.024.47026"},["b","16a"],["span.small","HEB"],"I waste away! Woe is me!"],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.16b","order":"02.24.024.47028"},["b","16b"],"Despite the rejoicing of the remnant, the prophet laments the destruction of the many peoples who rejected righteousness (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.16-18"},"vv. 16–18"],")."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.19a","order":"02.24.024.47030"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/earth-renewal-of"},"TG Earth, Renewal of"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.20a","order":"02.24.024.47032"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/last-days"},"TG Last Days"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.21a","order":"02.24.024.47034"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/day-of-the-lord"},"TG Day of the Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.21b","order":"02.24.024.47036"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/punish"},"TG Punish"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.22a","order":"02.24.024.47038"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/spirits-in-prison"},"TG Spirits in Prison"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.22b","order":"02.24.024.47040"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hell"},"TG Hell"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/salvation-for-the-dead"},"Salvation for the Dead"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.22c","order":"02.24.024.47042"},["b","22c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/5.25"},"John 5:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.23a","order":"02.24.024.47044"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.49"},"D&C 133:49"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.23b","order":"02.24.024.47046"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"23c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/24.23c","order":"02.24.024.47048"},["b","23c"],["span.small","OR"],"His elders in glory."]]}
